    Title: Hevajratantra
    Locus: 1
Tags:
  - 831
Commentary: Doctrine and Method combined in a 'mystic heat' that burns away
  ignorance. In Tibet this heat (gTum-mo) is even produced on a more exterior
  plane for bodily warmth.
---
The word ‘navel’ indicates the centre and the centre here is Avadhûti,
and here Candâlî burns.
